content: into first chain and then chain 3 counts as 1 treble_crochet and work the treble_crochet into the same space as the slip_stitch carry on from the first * once you have completed the trellis pattern work lace pattern as you did for the first half of the stole f inishing weave in all ends and block size when blocked 78 by 23 © 2008 yarnmistrys co uk kai mistry photography kai mistry & oliver rochford all rights reserved for personal use only
